:::Jetstorm/Sharpedge:::

::Sharpedge gets hit by the Autoguns, but Jetstorm dodges.  Sharpedge dodges 
the missles and shoots 2 missles at Dark One.  Jetstorm sees Nemises 
Enforcers streategy on using his wings as shields.  He blocks the shots with 
his wing, which was still kicking.  he fired 25 energy blasts and 25 rapid 
fire optic blasts at Nemises Enforcer, hoping to destroy his wings so hed be 
more vulnerable.  They hear the retreat call::
Jetstorm: Say what?
Sharpedge: Damn! I almost had that Scattershot guy!
::Jetstorm transforms in jet mode and flies out, while Sharpedge limps back 
to the Chosen Mafia base::
